                                    <h1>Recording Schedule Overlay</h1>
                                    <p class="intro">
                                      This is the schedule that will be used for <a href="/Web_User_Interface/720p_Series/Recording/Video/">planned recordings</a> and the <a href="/Web_User_Interface/720p_Series/Recording/Photoseries/">photoseries</a>. Just select the service you want to use and fill out a time window for this function to be active in. Every blue block inside the schedule stands for a 30min window of activity. Please make sure that the camera is set to the correct <a href="/Web_User_Interface/720p_Series/System/Date_Time/">Time Zone</a> and that the Daylight-Saving Time parameter is set correctly.
                                    </p>
